WEBVTT

01:49.759 --> 01:50.520
Students,

01:51.039 --> 01:52.920
we will have a self-study class next period.

01:52.920 --> 01:54.120
Ask questions if you don't understand.

01:54.120 --> 01:56.920
Class monitor, write down whoever makes trouble.

01:56.920 --> 01:57.640
Class dismissed.

01:57.640 --> 01:58.479
Stand up.

01:59.039 --> 02:01.800
Goodbye, teacher.

02:02.000 --> 02:03.130
Goodbye, students.

02:09.400 --> 02:09.919
Dude,

02:10.000 --> 02:11.520
could you explain this question to me?

02:11.520 --> 02:12.850
I don't know how to do it.

02:13.960 --> 02:15.640
Tell me. I really don't know.

02:16.960 --> 02:18.640
Will this really work?

02:18.800 --> 02:20.160
You'll see in a minute.

02:21.160 --> 02:22.600
Explain this question to me too.

02:22.600 --> 02:23.730
I don't know either.

02:25.920 --> 02:28.579
Jingu, I don't quite know this question either.

02:30.800 --> 02:31.660
Brother Jingu,

02:32.520 --> 02:34.960
can you explain this question to me?

02:36.720 --> 02:37.400
Jingu.

02:40.120 --> 02:42.050
I don't know this question either.

02:43.520 --> 02:45.450
I don't know this question either.

02:48.880 --> 02:51.140
I think I have questions I don't know too.

02:57.120 --> 02:58.079
Well,

02:58.640 --> 03:00.300
you have questions to ask too?

03:02.080 --> 03:02.920
Deskmate.

03:03.160 --> 03:05.840
I know because of Xinrui,

03:06.040 --> 03:08.170
you've always had a knot in your heart.

03:08.320 --> 03:09.880
But it's in the past.

03:10.520 --> 03:11.920
Mutou and I have let it go.

03:12.760 --> 03:14.090
You should let it go too.

03:14.320 --> 03:15.920
We're all classmates.

03:16.320 --> 03:18.480
If you distance yourself from us on purpose,

03:18.480 --> 03:20.040
we'll be very sad too.

03:20.360 --> 03:22.320
I'm not distancing myself from you.

03:22.320 --> 03:23.160
It's just that

03:24.200 --> 03:25.730
I don't know how to face you.

03:27.280 --> 03:29.079
We've been classmates for so many years.

03:29.079 --> 03:31.160
Let's put those petty things aside.

03:31.280 --> 03:32.800
We're still good brothers.

03:32.800 --> 03:33.480
Exactly.

03:33.520 --> 03:34.880
We are the five Zhicheng brothers.

03:34.880 --> 03:36.880
We can't do without any of us, right?

03:41.079 --> 03:42.010
It's break time.

03:42.160 --> 03:43.220
Want to play a game?

03:43.280 --> 03:44.040
Do you dare?

03:47.160 --> 03:48.400
Come on, Alpha.

03:53.840 --> 03:54.680
Great.

03:59.160 --> 04:00.760
Okay.

04:06.400 --> 04:08.280
Come on.

04:08.360 --> 04:10.240
Come on.

04:21.200 --> 04:22.360
Okay.

04:24.240 --> 04:25.560
Time never speaks,

04:26.280 --> 04:28.000
but it heals everything.

04:33.480 --> 04:34.280
Sorry.

04:35.280 --> 04:36.120
Qiao Yan.

04:36.920 --> 04:38.780
What's wrong? Why are you crying?

04:40.520 --> 04:41.400
Nothing.

04:42.480 --> 04:43.680
I just had a fight with my mom

04:43.680 --> 04:44.800
and she scolded me.

04:46.360 --> 04:47.440
I get scolded a lot.

04:47.560 --> 04:48.760
You'll get used to it.

04:49.080 --> 04:51.940
Where are you going alone in the middle of the night?

04:51.960 --> 04:52.880
I don't know.

04:53.280 --> 04:54.720
You had a fight with your parents,

04:54.720 --> 04:56.240
ran away from home, and don't know where to go.

04:56.240 --> 04:56.800
Right?

04:56.840 --> 04:58.200
I can tell you lack experience in this.

04:58.200 --> 04:59.240
I have experience.

04:59.240 --> 05:01.300
Come on, I'll take you to a good place.

05:01.800 --> 05:02.600
Where?

05:07.920 --> 05:08.920
You did very well.

05:09.080 --> 05:09.720
Grandma,

05:10.600 --> 05:12.120
how many times have you watched this?

05:12.120 --> 05:13.280
You're still watching it.

05:13.280 --> 05:14.520
It's a good show.

05:14.720 --> 05:16.120
The acting is great.

05:17.960 --> 05:18.640
Grandma,

05:19.200 --> 05:21.200
I heard that tomorrow afternoon,

05:21.360 --> 05:23.520
Shenghuo Supermarket is having a promotion.

05:23.520 --> 05:25.360
They're giving away free eggs if you line up.

05:25.360 --> 05:26.290
Do you want to go?

05:26.680 --> 05:27.320
What time?

05:27.600 --> 05:28.730
How many per person?

05:29.080 --> 05:30.440
Tomorrow at 3:00 p.m.

05:30.520 --> 05:32.250
I don't know how many we can get.

05:33.360 --> 05:35.020
Grandma, where are you going?

05:35.120 --> 05:37.200
Getting a bag to collect the eggs.

05:43.440 --> 05:44.700
Here, have some water.

05:54.800 --> 05:56.200
What happened to you?

05:56.560 --> 05:57.840
Nothing.

05:58.400 --> 06:00.860
I just bumped into something accidentally.

06:01.720 --> 06:04.200
You're a girl but you have more injuries than a boy.

06:04.200 --> 06:05.800
You're quite tough.

06:09.480 --> 06:10.480
Shang Ningyu,

06:11.240 --> 06:13.570
have you ever thought about running away?

06:14.320 --> 06:15.520
Running away?

06:15.720 --> 06:17.000
Where to?

06:17.520 --> 06:18.480
Like,

06:19.040 --> 06:20.840
to a place where no one knows you,

06:20.880 --> 06:22.120
and start a new life.

06:22.360 --> 06:24.600
That won't work. I can't stay idle.

06:24.800 --> 06:25.720
If I don't have family

06:25.720 --> 06:27.120
or friends to talk to,

06:27.480 --> 06:28.680
I'll go crazy.

06:32.000 --> 06:33.360
I think I'm sick.

06:34.520 --> 06:36.400
Sick? What's wrong?

06:36.560 --> 06:38.000
Have you seen a doctor?

06:38.560 --> 06:40.120
What are your symptoms?

06:40.280 --> 06:41.720
Well,

06:43.880 --> 06:46.760
I've been feeling depressed all the time

06:47.960 --> 06:50.360
and staying awake all night.

06:52.200 --> 06:54.460
Not being able to sleep isn't an illness.

06:54.600 --> 06:56.320
You just have too much pressure from studying.

06:56.320 --> 06:58.560
Working so hard, no wonder you can't sleep well.

06:58.560 --> 06:59.240
By the way,

06:59.320 --> 07:00.280
in a few days, Mr. Men

07:00.280 --> 07:02.010
is taking everyone out, right?

07:02.040 --> 07:02.800
To go camping.

07:02.800 --> 07:04.060
You should come along.

07:04.240 --> 07:05.120
Camping?

07:06.360 --> 07:07.120
Where to?

07:07.240 --> 07:08.300
Ronghua Mountain.

07:08.960 --> 07:11.560
I heard there'll be a meteor shower that night.

07:13.440 --> 07:15.960
Going to see the meteor shower with you

07:16.040 --> 07:18.320
as it falls on this earth.

07:19.440 --> 07:21.000
Go mountain climbing.

07:34.040 --> 07:34.720
Where is it?

07:34.760 --> 07:35.820
It's fine. Come in.

07:36.000 --> 07:37.600
Um, hello.

07:37.640 --> 07:39.800
Where can I get the free eggs?

07:39.880 --> 07:41.610
All the way inside, turn right.

07:42.280 --> 07:43.600
Thank you. Thank you.

07:43.640 --> 07:44.570
You're welcome.

07:55.200 --> 07:55.760
What are you doing?

07:55.760 --> 07:57.120
I... I'm not buying this.

07:57.120 --> 07:57.760
Grandma.

07:57.960 --> 07:59.440
You're the lucky winner of our event.

07:59.440 --> 08:01.360
You need to collect the eggs with a sense of ceremony.

08:01.360 --> 08:02.520
This scarf is for you.

08:02.520 --> 08:03.400
For me?

08:04.720 --> 08:05.800
It's pretty nice.

08:06.760 --> 08:08.320
All right. Thank you.

08:10.000 --> 08:11.060
Where are the eggs?

08:11.120 --> 08:11.720
This way.

08:31.120 --> 08:32.559
Look here, Grandma.

08:55.200 --> 08:57.800
We are already at this age.

08:58.200 --> 09:01.360
How much more good time do we have left to waste?

09:01.640 --> 09:02.360
Wenying.

09:02.760 --> 09:04.090
Every day in the future,

09:04.360 --> 09:06.690
are you willing to let me spend it with you?

09:07.160 --> 09:07.880
Romantic,

09:08.560 --> 09:09.360
warm,

09:10.200 --> 09:11.080
and loving.

09:14.360 --> 09:16.160
Grandpa, Grandma, I know

09:16.440 --> 09:17.240
that in your era,

09:17.240 --> 09:18.800
expressing feelings was implicit

09:18.800 --> 09:20.060
and you might feel shy.

09:20.080 --> 09:21.880
So we took the liberty

09:22.040 --> 09:23.800
of planning this surprise for you.

09:23.800 --> 09:24.800
I hope you like it.

09:25.480 --> 09:27.160
We also sincerely hope

09:27.760 --> 09:29.320
that in the days to come,

09:29.680 --> 09:31.540
the life you live can be romantic,

09:31.600 --> 09:32.240
warm,

09:32.400 --> 09:33.400
and full of love.

09:34.440 --> 09:35.680
Well, um,

09:36.600 --> 09:40.320
I should go back and ask my granddaughter

09:40.680 --> 09:41.680
and family first.

09:43.480 --> 09:44.480
Grandma!

09:53.160 --> 09:54.160
Grandma!

09:55.600 --> 09:56.640
I support you!

09:59.000 --> 10:01.200
Grandma, I support you too!

10:04.640 --> 10:07.840
Grandma, we all support you.

10:10.360 --> 10:11.080
Grandma.

10:11.680 --> 10:12.920
For over ten years,

10:13.480 --> 10:16.080
you have raised me with complete devotion.

10:16.400 --> 10:17.320
I really don't know

10:17.320 --> 10:19.040
how to repay you.

10:19.960 --> 10:21.600
I'm about to go to college

10:22.040 --> 10:23.770
and we'll go our separate ways.

10:23.840 --> 10:26.000
If there's no one to love

10:26.120 --> 10:27.480
and take care of you,

10:27.960 --> 10:29.720
how can I be at ease?

10:31.480 --> 10:34.680
Thank you, child. I will listen to you.

10:35.560 --> 10:38.600
I still want to help raise your children.

10:39.320 --> 10:40.080
Wenying.

10:40.720 --> 10:41.440
I'm here.

10:41.720 --> 10:42.800
Let me stay with you

10:42.840 --> 10:44.760
and take care of our grandchildren.

10:44.760 --> 10:45.560
Okay?

12:14.680 --> 12:17.080
Grandma, it's been so many years.

12:17.760 --> 12:20.240
I finally see you smiling so happily again.

12:20.720 --> 12:21.560
That's great.

12:22.800 --> 12:25.360
From now on, you two are real brothers.

12:26.400 --> 12:28.200
I'm even your older brother now.

12:30.320 --> 12:32.480
Did you hit a girl or not?

12:33.800 --> 12:35.400
You don't even believe your brother.

12:35.400 --> 12:36.720
We've known each other for so long.

12:36.720 --> 12:38.850
Don't you know what kind of person I am?

12:39.000 --> 12:40.600
True.

12:41.680 --> 12:42.840
In that case,

12:43.120 --> 12:44.580
I have two older brothers.

12:44.960 --> 12:46.890
Let's see who dares to bully me now.

12:49.080 --> 12:52.280
So who is older?

12:52.720 --> 12:55.320
Who is the older brother and who is the younger?

12:56.880 --> 12:58.240
Of course I'm the older brother.

12:58.240 --> 12:59.640
He is my younger brother.

12:59.680 --> 13:01.360
Come on, call me brother.

13:03.440 --> 13:05.240
Bro, bro, bro.

13:06.160 --> 13:07.120
Good boy.

13:08.240 --> 13:10.000
But the way you call me

13:10.080 --> 13:11.740
sounds like a hen laying eggs.

13:13.720 --> 13:16.880
Who are you calling a mother hen laying eggs?

13:16.880 --> 13:18.080
Stop messing around.

13:21.080 --> 13:21.920
Gong Yu,

13:22.320 --> 13:24.640
I used to be rude to you.

13:25.080 --> 13:26.340
Don't take it to heart.

13:27.080 --> 13:28.740
It's fine. That's in the past.

13:28.920 --> 13:30.880
Do you think I'm that fragile?

13:32.760 --> 13:35.040
But when I join the army,

13:35.720 --> 13:36.760
I hope you can help

13:37.040 --> 13:38.800
take care of my grandpa.

13:39.480 --> 13:40.540
You are my brother,

13:40.840 --> 13:42.400
and Mutou is your younger brother.

13:42.400 --> 13:43.360
With us around,

13:43.480 --> 13:45.440
you can safely leave Grandpa Gong to us.

13:45.440 --> 13:46.240
Right, Mutou?

13:46.320 --> 13:46.920
Yes.

13:47.240 --> 13:48.840
We will take good care of him.

13:49.120 --> 13:49.720
Thanks.

13:53.240 --> 13:54.400
As for Ruirui,

13:55.400 --> 13:57.120
do you want to talk to her?

13:57.360 --> 13:58.640
I know what you mean.

13:59.320 --> 14:01.240
On the day of the New Year's Eve camping,

14:01.240 --> 14:02.970
I will have a good talk with her.

14:12.840 --> 14:13.560
Yuanbao,

14:14.160 --> 14:16.490
when is Grandpa Gong moving to your house?

14:17.200 --> 14:18.080
Not yet.

14:18.280 --> 14:20.480
He said he'll move after New Year's Day.

14:20.680 --> 14:21.760
Then will Gong Yu

14:21.840 --> 14:23.840
stay at your house during holidays?

14:25.080 --> 14:25.800
I don't think so.

14:25.800 --> 14:27.200
There's no place to stay.

14:27.760 --> 14:28.920
That makes sense.

14:51.120 --> 14:52.560
Shang Ningyu, what are you looking at?

14:52.560 --> 14:54.280
N-Nothing.

14:54.640 --> 14:55.370
Give it to me.

15:00.200 --> 15:02.200
You can't even remember Newton's laws.

15:02.200 --> 15:03.360
You still have time to read this?

15:03.360 --> 15:04.440
With your level,

15:04.760 --> 15:07.290
can you even understand a military magazine?

15:11.200 --> 15:11.960
Class,

15:12.600 --> 15:15.120
the day after tomorrow is the last day of 2007.

15:15.120 --> 15:16.720
The day after that is New Year's Day.

15:16.720 --> 15:18.160
Those of you going camping

15:18.160 --> 15:19.200
must wear more clothes.

15:19.200 --> 15:20.280
The class monitor will

15:20.280 --> 15:22.200
distribute the guidelines to everyone.

15:22.200 --> 15:23.330
Have fun, everyone.

15:42.000 --> 15:43.360
Wait for me. I can't carry this anymore.

15:43.360 --> 15:45.090
Yuanbao, let's go to that room.

15:45.280 --> 15:46.280
I can't carry this anymore.

15:46.280 --> 15:47.960
Awesome.

15:52.080 --> 15:52.800
Class.

15:54.080 --> 15:55.760
Without delaying your studies,

15:55.760 --> 15:56.920
to cheer you up,

15:57.200 --> 15:59.260
I'm taking you to see a meteor shower.

16:00.600 --> 16:01.320
Today,

16:01.640 --> 16:03.440
you don't have to treat me as your teacher.

16:03.440 --> 16:05.080
I won't teach you anything about studying either.

16:05.080 --> 16:06.280
Just have fun.

16:09.200 --> 16:10.840
Wait, note two things.

16:11.040 --> 16:11.720
First,

16:12.000 --> 16:13.040
no littering.

16:13.320 --> 16:14.560
Second, be safe.

16:14.720 --> 16:15.280
Go play.

16:20.560 --> 16:22.760
This is pretty. Take it for decoration.

16:24.240 --> 16:25.160
My grandpa asked me

16:25.160 --> 16:26.200
to bring you guys lots of good food.

16:26.200 --> 16:27.280
I'll share it with you later.

16:27.280 --> 16:28.080
Really?

16:30.320 --> 16:31.800
If Yuanbao hears this,

16:32.120 --> 16:33.250
she'll be thrilled.

16:33.800 --> 16:35.000
Thank Grandpa for us.

16:36.040 --> 16:38.120
That secret you whispered in my ear,

16:38.240 --> 16:39.200
does she know it?

16:40.840 --> 16:42.000
I said it's a secret.

16:42.600 --> 16:43.860
You can't let her know.

16:44.400 --> 16:46.860
Don't betray me now that you're her brother.

16:48.400 --> 16:50.130
You're the top guy of Zhicheng,

16:50.200 --> 16:51.600
and you're still afraid?

16:57.240 --> 16:58.160
Hurry up, Yuanbao.

16:58.160 --> 16:59.760
Hurry up and tidy up these snacks.

16:59.760 --> 17:00.440
Hurry.

17:01.120 --> 17:02.480
You guys outside, hurry up.

17:02.480 --> 17:04.079
Bring the snacks in.

17:04.119 --> 17:05.200
You're the only one talking.

17:05.200 --> 17:06.000
Where should I put this?

17:06.000 --> 17:07.640
I'm just urging you on.

17:07.800 --> 17:08.960
Class rep, let me help you.

17:08.960 --> 17:09.480
No, thanks.

17:09.480 --> 17:10.720
Now you know why you're fat.

17:10.720 --> 17:11.720
Put this over there.

17:11.720 --> 17:12.599
Put this here.

17:12.640 --> 17:14.000
This is mine.

17:14.240 --> 17:15.240
Bring it here.

17:15.599 --> 17:16.400
Yuanbao.

17:17.440 --> 17:18.200
What is it?

17:26.160 --> 17:27.619
Matching couple outfits!

17:28.680 --> 17:29.840
Not bad, Meng Jingu.

17:29.880 --> 17:30.760
When did this happen?

17:30.760 --> 17:32.560
I really didn't see this coming.

17:32.600 --> 17:34.060
What a pleasant surprise!

17:37.520 --> 17:39.040
Put your clothes on properly, don't catch a cold.

17:39.040 --> 17:39.800
Be careful.

17:46.960 --> 17:48.420
Put this on, don't freeze.

17:48.520 --> 17:49.780
Come on, let's tidy up.

17:51.200 --> 17:52.400
I'm late.

17:54.880 --> 17:55.560
Qiao Yan.

17:55.760 --> 17:57.520
Your clothes look so good.

17:57.720 --> 17:59.120
Your clothes look great.

17:59.200 --> 18:00.200
Where did you buy them?

18:00.200 --> 18:01.360
Can you tell me?

18:01.920 --> 18:03.640
Why did you buy so many things?

18:03.720 --> 18:04.920
Here, give them to me.

18:05.040 --> 18:06.560
I bought some snacks for everyone.

18:06.560 --> 18:08.160
We already bought a lot.

18:08.280 --> 18:09.760
Don't let them go to waste.

18:12.040 --> 18:14.680
I'm usually not very nice with my words.

18:15.000 --> 18:17.760
I might have unintentionally hurt everyone's feelings.

18:17.760 --> 18:19.440
I wanted to buy more snacks

18:19.520 --> 18:20.440
as an apology.

18:20.840 --> 18:21.840
What are you talking about?

18:21.840 --> 18:22.920
We are all friends.

18:23.000 --> 18:24.200
No need to be so polite.

18:24.200 --> 18:25.880
Come on, let's tidy up together.

18:25.880 --> 18:27.080
I heard on the news

18:27.120 --> 18:29.320
that the meteor shower isn't until eleven.

18:29.320 --> 18:30.720
Come on.

18:34.240 --> 18:35.280
Ruirui.

18:35.800 --> 18:37.560
I hid a can of delicious snacks for you.

18:37.560 --> 18:38.890
What delicious snacks?

18:43.080 --> 18:43.720
Potato chips.

18:43.720 --> 18:45.250
Aren't they your favorite?

18:59.520 --> 19:02.050
Grandpa asked me to bring you two some snacks.

19:02.280 --> 19:03.520
Thank you, Grandpa.

19:06.160 --> 19:07.160
Not thanking me?

19:09.360 --> 19:10.490
Thank you, brother.

19:10.800 --> 19:12.280
Good girl, eat up.

19:15.280 --> 19:16.410
Let's eat together.

19:18.920 --> 19:19.600
Jingu.

19:26.320 --> 19:27.080
What are you listening to?

19:27.080 --> 19:28.080
Let me listen too.

19:42.160 --> 19:44.040
Well, I like listening to music too.

19:44.040 --> 19:44.800
Make some room.

19:44.800 --> 19:45.800
Let me listen too.

19:45.880 --> 19:47.610
What song are you listening to?

19:50.320 --> 19:51.440
Nice earphones.

19:55.480 --> 19:56.280
A love song?

19:56.560 --> 19:58.160
It just shuffled to this one.

20:16.840 --> 20:18.500
You're going to join the army?

20:19.360 --> 20:20.200
That's great.

20:20.320 --> 20:21.780
Yes, I'm joining the army.

20:36.320 --> 20:37.280
You're leaving?

20:38.760 --> 20:40.020
I'm leaving next week.

20:50.120 --> 20:51.680
Come on, let's talk.

20:57.280 --> 20:58.760
Well, you guys talk first.

20:58.840 --> 21:00.300
I'm going to the restroom.

21:06.280 --> 21:07.560
During this time,

21:08.120 --> 21:09.600
I've been deeply moved.

21:11.040 --> 21:12.080
Seeing

21:12.640 --> 21:15.040
how sincerely you do things for each other,

21:15.560 --> 21:17.200
I feel really satisfied.

21:17.400 --> 21:18.920
To be a part of your group,

21:19.760 --> 21:20.620
I'm very happy.

21:24.280 --> 21:26.640
But just as I realized how great everyone is,

21:26.640 --> 21:27.560
I have to leave.

21:29.120 --> 21:30.850
Why do you want to join the army?

21:31.600 --> 21:33.400
I've always wanted to win glory for my country,

21:33.400 --> 21:34.320
so I can be like my father

21:34.320 --> 21:35.450
and become a soldier

21:35.720 --> 21:36.980
to defend the country.

21:40.240 --> 21:41.160
I heard

21:41.960 --> 21:42.890
that your father

21:44.160 --> 21:45.000
passed away.

21:47.760 --> 21:50.420
He sacrificed himself to save a drowning child.

21:52.280 --> 21:53.200
But in my heart,

21:53.680 --> 21:55.010
he has always been a hero

21:55.600 --> 21:58.200
and the role model I want to be for my whole life.

21:58.280 --> 21:59.920
I also hope your dream comes true

21:59.920 --> 22:01.720
and you become an angel in white.

22:03.840 --> 22:04.840
I'll work hard.

22:05.720 --> 22:06.600
Actually,

22:07.200 --> 22:09.260
what I really want to say today is that

22:10.800 --> 22:12.260
whether it's friendship,

22:12.600 --> 22:13.330
family love,

22:13.600 --> 22:16.440
or those feelings we don't quite understand yet,

22:16.880 --> 22:19.010
they are all very precious affections

22:20.960 --> 22:23.720
and wonderful connections between people.

22:24.400 --> 22:27.320
We can cherish this friendship between us.

22:28.520 --> 22:29.280
And you

22:29.800 --> 22:32.520
shouldn't ignore other people's feelings anymore.

22:32.520 --> 22:34.880
O-Other people?

22:37.480 --> 22:40.280
Like the person hiding behind the tree behind you.

22:49.440 --> 22:51.440
In fact, between people,

22:51.520 --> 22:54.050
there are not that many insurmountable gaps.

22:54.080 --> 22:55.960
Sometimes, a reminder

22:56.160 --> 22:57.280
or a joke

22:57.560 --> 22:59.400
is enough to eliminate the estrangement between us,

22:59.400 --> 23:00.840
so we can open our hearts to each other

23:00.840 --> 23:02.300
and become close friends.

23:02.440 --> 23:05.080
Perhaps this is the charm of youth,

23:05.400 --> 23:06.880
simple and pure.

23:11.880 --> 23:14.440
Is Gong Yu really going to join the army?

23:16.120 --> 23:18.040
Yes, he's leaving in a few days.

23:18.720 --> 23:22.000
Fortunately, he doesn't have to worry about his grandfather anymore.

23:22.000 --> 23:23.840
Actually, he's a really nice guy,

23:23.840 --> 23:25.680
just not good at expressing himself.

23:25.680 --> 23:27.280
When others misunderstand him,

23:27.280 --> 23:28.880
he doesn't explain too much.

23:31.040 --> 23:33.280
The things I did to him before,

23:33.520 --> 23:35.400
I hope he really doesn't mind.

23:35.720 --> 23:36.600
All right.

23:37.400 --> 23:39.000
Gong Yu is not a petty person.

23:39.920 --> 23:41.780
This is also a good lesson for you.

23:42.040 --> 23:43.680
You can't be so arbitrary in the future,

23:43.680 --> 23:44.480
got it?

23:45.720 --> 23:46.480
Got it.

23:48.560 --> 23:49.360
In a few years,

23:49.560 --> 23:51.290
when we go to school out of town,

23:51.440 --> 23:53.970
Grandma will at least have someone to talk to.

23:54.400 --> 23:56.200
You don't need to worry too much.

23:57.680 --> 23:59.280
I think it's pretty good too.

24:07.440 --> 24:10.000
Look, everyone! The meteor shower is here.

24:10.200 --> 24:11.440
Look over there!

24:12.040 --> 24:13.000
Hurry!

24:13.440 --> 24:14.200
Come here!

24:21.760 --> 24:22.720
Make a wish!

24:24.120 --> 24:26.800
I hope Grandma, Grandpa, Uncle, Aunt,

24:27.040 --> 24:28.000
and Mutou,

24:28.120 --> 24:30.200
will all be safe and healthy,

24:30.360 --> 24:32.360
and stay happily together forever.

24:32.520 --> 24:33.640
Also,

24:33.800 --> 24:35.120
I hope Mutou and I

24:35.320 --> 24:37.180
can get into an ideal university,

24:37.200 --> 24:40.320
and have a bright and beautiful future.

24:42.160 --> 24:44.680
I hope Yuanbao's wishes all come true.

24:45.560 --> 24:47.720
I hope I can get into

24:47.800 --> 24:49.640
the Physics Department of Qingbei University as I wish.

24:49.640 --> 24:52.800
I also hope my friends' dreams come true.

24:54.040 --> 24:56.640
I hope my children stay safe and healthy

24:56.840 --> 24:58.760
and get into their ideal universities.

24:58.760 --> 24:59.560
Also,

25:00.320 --> 25:03.000
when will I stop being single?

25:03.280 --> 25:05.200
I hope my dad will agree

25:05.200 --> 25:07.040
to let me buy those new sneakers.

25:07.560 --> 25:08.560
I hope next year

25:08.680 --> 25:10.800
my cultivation level will improve,

25:11.240 --> 25:13.240
and I can understand Qimen Dunjia.

25:13.680 --> 25:15.210
Tuibeitu would be fine too.

25:15.480 --> 25:16.810
The I Ching is also okay.

25:22.040 --> 25:25.080
May all the wishes of the people I love come true.

25:25.640 --> 25:28.760
I hope I can be happy every day,

25:28.880 --> 25:31.440
and always have a bright smile.

25:32.360 --> 25:35.040
I hope everyone who likes me,

25:35.200 --> 25:37.200
and everyone I like,

25:37.600 --> 25:40.680
can be safe, happy, and achieve their dreams.

25:41.240 --> 25:42.360
I hope Tong Ruirui

25:42.480 --> 25:44.360
will notice me one day.

25:46.080 --> 25:49.400
I hope I can be happy in my next life.

25:52.720 --> 25:53.440
Nine.

25:54.680 --> 25:55.320
Seven.

25:55.560 --> 25:56.120
Six.

26:01.040 --> 26:03.760
Happy New Year!

26:04.000 --> 26:08.760
2008, here we come!

26:11.040 --> 26:14.920
2008, wishing my classmates a bright future.

26:15.520 --> 26:19.280
2008, I hope we can always be together.

26:19.720 --> 26:23.040
2008, let me have more PE classes.

26:23.400 --> 26:26.080
2008, make it to the top eight.

26:26.200 --> 26:29.280
2008, I want a holiday every day.

26:35.440 --> 26:37.520
2008, keep going.

26:38.960 --> 26:41.690
I hope everyone around me gets better and better.

26:42.640 --> 26:44.920
2008, victory in the Olympics!

26:45.760 --> 26:48.480
2008, I hope I can grow a bit taller.

26:49.000 --> 26:51.880
2008, I hope you stay healthy.

26:54.000 --> 26:56.640
I hope everyone's wishes come true.

27:07.800 --> 27:09.330
That silly girl Tong Ruirui

27:09.800 --> 27:11.130
is sleeping so soundly.

27:11.440 --> 27:12.500
I can't wake her up.

27:14.400 --> 27:16.000
In the middle of nowhere,

27:16.600 --> 27:19.000
I dared to go to the bathroom alone.

27:19.480 --> 27:22.120
I can brag about this to Mutou for a year.

27:23.040 --> 27:23.880
It's so cold.

27:30.400 --> 27:31.120
Qiao Yan.

27:32.040 --> 27:33.700
Are you going to the bathroom?

27:33.840 --> 27:35.800
It's so dark. I'll go with you.

27:35.920 --> 27:37.640
It's not safe for you to go alone.

27:37.640 --> 27:38.640
No need, Yuanbao.

27:38.840 --> 27:40.040
I can go by myself.

27:40.080 --> 27:40.800
Thank you.

27:40.880 --> 27:42.960
It's fine. I just came back from there.

27:42.960 --> 27:44.820
The road is really hard to walk on.

27:45.080 --> 27:45.720
Besides,

27:45.800 --> 27:47.800
we can keep each other company.

27:48.000 --> 27:49.530
It's fine. I'll go with you.

27:49.600 --> 27:50.680
I'm not sleepy anyway.

27:50.680 --> 27:52.340
I have nothing to be afraid of.

27:53.440 --> 27:56.040
Yuanbao, I just can't sleep.

27:56.080 --> 27:57.610
I want to get some fresh air.

27:57.720 --> 27:59.180
I'll just walk around here

27:59.280 --> 28:00.540
and won't go anywhere.

28:00.960 --> 28:02.160
Don't worry about me.

28:02.320 --> 28:03.280
Qiao Yan,

28:04.000 --> 28:05.600
you don't look well.

28:06.320 --> 28:07.440
Are you okay?

28:08.840 --> 28:09.560
I'm fine.

28:10.360 --> 28:11.920
I really just can't sleep.

28:12.720 --> 28:13.960
Go back and rest.

28:14.080 --> 28:14.840
Go to sleep.

28:14.880 --> 28:16.080
Don't worry about me.

28:16.600 --> 28:17.440
Okay.

28:18.040 --> 28:19.520
Then be careful.

28:20.000 --> 28:22.000
It's cold in the mountains at night.

28:22.000 --> 28:23.160
You're wearing so little.

28:23.160 --> 28:24.560
What if you catch a cold?

28:25.440 --> 28:26.000
Right,

28:26.360 --> 28:27.960
remember to take your phone.

28:28.240 --> 28:30.120
Call me if anything happens.

28:30.280 --> 28:31.120
Got it?

28:35.040 --> 28:35.800
Yuanbao.

28:37.000 --> 28:37.960
I used to

28:38.920 --> 28:40.600
badmouth you a lot

28:41.560 --> 28:42.600
and picked on you.

28:43.680 --> 28:44.440
I'm sorry.

28:45.440 --> 28:47.320
That's in the past.

28:47.400 --> 28:49.080
Why bring it up now?

28:50.880 --> 28:51.800
I just

28:53.120 --> 28:54.480
feel a little guilty.

28:54.960 --> 28:55.720
It's fine.

28:56.360 --> 28:58.240
You know I don't hold grudges.

28:58.680 --> 28:59.480
Besides,

28:59.760 --> 29:01.240
I know you too well.

29:01.800 --> 29:03.960
You may have a sharp tongue,

29:04.240 --> 29:05.920
but if I'm bullied,

29:06.320 --> 29:07.000
every time

29:07.120 --> 29:09.450
you're always the first to stand up for me.

29:10.760 --> 29:11.520
Yuanbao,

29:16.080 --> 29:19.160
being your classmate and friend

29:20.280 --> 29:21.410
makes me very happy.

29:23.120 --> 29:25.480
Why are you suddenly being so cheesy?

29:28.880 --> 29:29.360
It's nothing.

29:29.360 --> 29:32.080
I'm just being a little sentimental.

29:33.160 --> 29:34.960
What's there to be sentimental about?

29:34.960 --> 29:36.560
Winter break is coming soon.

29:36.600 --> 29:37.720
During the New Year,

29:37.720 --> 29:38.840
I'll call Shang Ningyu and Tong Ruirui,

29:38.840 --> 29:39.840
and we'll all go out.

29:39.840 --> 29:41.040
We can hang out for a day,

29:41.040 --> 29:43.040
and all our worries will disappear.

29:44.280 --> 29:46.480
Alright, I'm going back to sleep.

29:46.880 --> 29:48.080
Rest early.

29:48.240 --> 29:49.500
Don't go too far, okay?

29:52.080 --> 29:53.840
Okay, I'm going back.

29:55.760 --> 29:56.560
Yuanbao.

29:58.960 --> 29:59.820
Happy New Year.

30:00.800 --> 30:01.680
Happy New Year.

30:52.720 --> 30:53.640
Zaozao.

30:54.680 --> 30:56.240
That little lazy pig is not awake yet.

30:56.240 --> 30:56.920
Yuanbao.

30:56.960 --> 30:58.560
She was gone before I got up.

30:58.760 --> 31:00.560
I guess she went to the bathroom.

31:01.200 --> 31:02.330
Morning, everyone.

31:04.240 --> 31:06.900
The morning air on the mountain is really fresh.

31:11.640 --> 31:12.440
What's wrong?

31:13.760 --> 31:14.920
She's not answering.

31:14.920 --> 31:15.520
Ruirui,

31:15.880 --> 31:16.680
why don't you

31:16.760 --> 31:18.920
go to the restroom to look for her?

31:19.160 --> 31:20.360
I'm a little worried.

31:20.600 --> 31:22.120
Okay, I'll go take a look.

31:27.360 --> 31:28.840
She's an adult. What's there to worry about?

31:28.840 --> 31:30.160
There's nothing to worry about.

31:30.160 --> 31:31.560
Qiao Yan is also not here.

31:31.800 --> 31:33.720
Could they have left together?

31:33.880 --> 31:35.010
Qiao Yan is not here.

31:36.440 --> 31:37.680
Well, brother,

31:37.760 --> 31:39.840
why don't you give Qiao Yan a call?

31:40.160 --> 31:40.720
I'll call.

31:40.720 --> 31:42.520
Could it be that they were carried away

31:42.520 --> 31:44.450
by a bear in the middle of the night?

31:53.560 --> 31:55.040
She is not in the bathroom.

32:06.880 --> 32:08.080
She didn't bring her phone.

32:08.080 --> 32:09.880
And she left two letters behind.

32:11.800 --> 32:12.800
Could she have...

32:15.480 --> 32:17.840
Yaqi, go to the park administration for help.

32:17.840 --> 32:19.600
Tong Ruirui, go find Mr. Tian.

32:19.640 --> 32:21.570
Notify the school and her parents.

32:22.880 --> 32:23.280
Shang Ningyu.

32:23.280 --> 32:24.400
Wake everyone up.

32:24.400 --> 32:25.400
We'll split into four groups now.

32:25.400 --> 32:26.600
Hurry up and find her.

32:26.600 --> 32:27.400
Okay, okay.

32:29.200 --> 32:30.040
Nightfall.

32:31.280 --> 32:32.160
Starlight.

32:33.280 --> 32:34.120
City.

32:35.240 --> 32:36.000
Fireworks.

32:37.640 --> 32:38.370
Neon lights.

32:39.520 --> 32:42.250
There are so many beautiful things in this world,

32:43.000 --> 32:45.000
but none of them belong to me.

32:46.160 --> 32:47.800
God is so unfair.

32:48.760 --> 32:50.020
How dare you talk back!

32:50.440 --> 32:52.040
Talking back? I'll teach you to talk back!

32:52.040 --> 32:52.720
Take that!
